to being the father he once used to be!

184
00:12:45.431 --> 00:12:48.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But you... [breathes heavily]
It's all your fault!

185
00:12:49.185 --> 00:12:50.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts, sobs]

186
00:12:50.728 --> 00:12:53.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
