187
00:12:54.190 --> 00:12:56.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps] Why are you giving me that look?

188
00:12:57.694 --> 00:13:01.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Are you going to kill
me too? You're horrible!

189
00:13:01.656 --> 00:13:04.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[sobbing and screaming]

190
00:13:04.951 --> 00:13:07.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting]

