195
00:13:29.684 --> 00:13:31.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Ah!
-Hey!

196
00:13:32.020 --> 00:13:34.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Kotetsu laughs] Funny to see you
on this side of town!

197
00:13:34.772 --> 00:13:36.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Uh, hey, I'll have a Legend's Cola.

198
00:13:37.942 --> 00:13:39.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So... What did you want
to talk to me about?

199
00:13:40.236 --> 00:13:41.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Brace yourself.

200
00:13:41.362 --> 00:13:44.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I went ahead and did some digging to see
what I could uncover about NEXT

201
00:13:44.532 --> 00:13:48.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
that might have lost their powers.
And I came across something really big.

202
00:13:49.454 --> 00:13:50.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What is it?

203
00:13:51.831 --> 00:13:55.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
