but, as it turns out,

204
00:13:56.336 --> 00:13:59.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Legend also suffered
a decline in his powers.

205
00:13:59.672 --> 00:14:00.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Say what?!

206
00:14:04.594 --> 00:14:06.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey, come on, keep it down.

207
00:14:06.846 --> 00:14:11.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Uh, yeah, sorry. Oh, hey, Legend's Cola!
[chuckles] Thanks.

208
00:14:14.771 --> 00:14:18.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There's just no way that can be true!
Do you have any proof?

209
00:14:19.275 --> 00:14:22.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Ben] I recently spoke with a guy
that was a hero during Legend's time.

210
00:14:23.321 --> 00:14:25.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And they had no reason to lie to me.

211
00:14:25.573 --> 00:14:29.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
That's crazy. Legend set a record
that no one could touch for years, Ben.

212
00:14:29.202 --> 00:14:32.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-A hero like that wouldn't be--
-Trust me. I know how you feel.

213
00:14:32.246 --> 00:14:35.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When I first found out, I certainly
didn't wanna believe it either.

214
00:14:35.750 --> 00:14:37.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Apparently when his powers started to go,

215
00:14:37.710 --> 00:14:40.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
they began staging the program
on a regular basis.

216
00:14:40.630 --> 00:14:43.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
