219
00:14:48.971 --> 00:14:53.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Ben] Not only that, they even went as far
as erasing any arrest records

220
00:14:53.184 --> 00:14:54.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
that made him look bad.

221
00:14:55.395 --> 00:14:57.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Kotetsu] So that's why there were
no records on Jake.

222
00:14:58.481 --> 00:15:01.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Ben] With his powers declining,
I guess he had no choice.

223
00:15:01.275 --> 00:15:04.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Otherwise, it would've been impossible
to remain at the top.

224
00:15:04.946 --> 00:15:07.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm told that Legend was torn up about it.

225
00:15:07.740 --> 00:15:10.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They say he drowned himself in alcohol.

226
00:15:11.953 --> 00:15:16.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So how are you holding up?
You notice any decline in your powers?

227
00:15:16.791 --> 00:15:17.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[sighs]

228
00:15:18.459 --> 00:15:19.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kotetsu] Yeah, sort of.

229
00:15:20.211 --> 00:15:23.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Ben] I see... Look, let me give
you some advice.

230
00:15:23.965 --> 00:15:26.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You should start thinking
about what to do with your life

231
00:15:27.093 --> 00:15:28.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
before you end up like Legend.

232
00:15:29.470 --> 00:15:31.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kotetsu] I don't wanna quit being a hero.

233
00:15:32.223 --> 00:15:34.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Ben] Hey, come on, I don't
want you to quit either.

234
00:15:35.184 --> 00:15:38.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But you and I both know
you can't continue this work forever...

235
00:15:39.355 --> 00:15:40.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kotetsu sighs]

236
00:15:40.648 --> 00:15:43.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Ben] Listen, I'm saying this
for your own good.

237
00:15:43.443 --> 00:15:45.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
