-[thud, clattering]

238
00:15:50.074 --> 00:15:51.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[sighs]

239
00:15:52.410 --> 00:15:53.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
