246
00:16:29.780 --> 00:16:32.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You have to be strong someday,
so you can punish evil.

247
00:16:32.658 --> 00:16:33.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Okay.

248
00:16:33.951 --> 00:16:36.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You'll be a chip off the old block, son.

249
00:16:36.746 --> 00:16:38.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
