What do you know about my pain?!

257
00:16:58.017 --> 00:16:59.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Mr. Legend] What I go through?
-[Origa whimpers]

258
00:16:59.852 --> 00:17:04.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
