I have to be strong, no matter what!

259
00:17:07.276 --> 00:17:09.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps, groans]

260
00:17:12.865 --> 00:17:14.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
