274
00:18:04.500 --> 00:18:05.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts]

275
00:18:09.422 --> 00:18:10.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
